509
00:25:24,620 --> 00:25:25,790
Great!

510
00:26:29,830 --> 00:26:31,700
I'm starving!

511
00:26:31,700 --> 00:26:33,430
Let's go find something to eat!

512
00:26:34,140 --> 00:26:34,760
I'm starving!

513
00:26:34,760 --> 00:26:36,960
