549
00:29:11,310 --> 00:29:13,040
A birthday gift is okay, right?

550
00:29:18,320 --> 00:29:19,080
Maybe

551
00:29:19,100 --> 00:29:20,510
we should go inside now.

552
00:29:21,420 --> 00:29:22,460
I like you.

553
00:29:26,140 --> 00:29:26,660
I...

554
00:29:26,790 --> 00:29:27,790
like...

555
00:29:28,550 --> 00:29:29,180
