563
00:29:50,140 --> 00:29:52,700
♪ Even mountains and seas
can't separate us ♪

564
00:29:53,350 --> 00:29:54,700
I just really want

565
00:29:53,400 --> 00:29:56,470
♪ I wish I could turn into a bird
to explore the world for you ♪

566
00:29:54,700 --> 00:29:55,180
to tell you

567
00:29:55,180 --> 00:29:55,620
I...

568
00:29:56,550 --> 00:29:57,510
I really, really,

569
00:29:57,070 --> 00:29:58,570
♪ The vast, boundless Milky Way ♪

570
00:29:57,660 --> 00:29:58,350
really,

571
00:29:58,610 --> 00:30:00,370
